11#ifndef RTC_BASE_CRC32_H_
12#define RTC_BASE_CRC32_H_
13
14#include <stddef.h>
15#include <stdint.h>
16
17#include <string>
18
19namespace rtc {
20
21// Updates a CRC32 checksum with |len| bytes from |buf|. |initial| holds the
22// checksum result from the previous update; for the first call, it should be 0.
23uint32_t UpdateCrc32(uint32_t initial, const void* buf, size_t len);
24
25// Computes a CRC32 checksum using |len| bytes from |buf|.
26inline uint32_t ComputeCrc32(const void* buf, size_t len) {
27 return UpdateCrc32(0, buf, len);
28}
29inline uint32_t ComputeCrc32(const std::string& str) {
30 return ComputeCrc32(str.c_str(), str.size());
31}
32
33} // namespace rtc
34
35#endif // RTC_BASE_CRC32_H_
